                  PsiPodVerbatimParagraphImpl(Perl5 POD: POD_VERBATIM_PARAGRAPH)
                    PsiElement(Perl5 POD: code)('  sub fetchrow {\n    # $what is one of fetchrow_{array,hashref}\n    my($self, $sth, $what) = @_;\n    if ($] < 5.008) {\n      return $sth->$what;\n    } else {\n      require Encode;\n      if (wantarray) {\n        my @arr = $sth->$what;\n        for (@arr) {\n          defined && /[^\000-\177]/ && Encode::_utf8_on($_);\n        }\n        return @arr;\n      } else {\n        my $ret = $sth->$what;\n        if (ref $ret) {\n          for my $k (keys %$ret) {\n            defined\n            && /[^\000-\177]/\n            && Encode::_utf8_on($_) for $ret->{$k};\n          }\n          return $ret;\n        } else {\n          defined && /[^\000-\177]/ && Encode::_utf8_on($_) for $ret;\n          return $ret;\n        }\n      }\n    }\n  }\n')
